Literature is replete with solar cells based on small molecules having acceptors and donors arranged various geometries such as X-shaped donor molecule22, star molecule23 and linear geometric molecules24, etc. In these molecules, the extended π-conjugation responsible for absorbance of non-fullerene have been enhanced via attachment of fluoro25,26, chloro and cyano groups over the skeleton structure. One if the most successful arrangement, is D–π\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
